It was Support Your Parks Weekend, so in spite of the cold temps, I was going to the park I was at US-10562 for this fun, but cold activation. The Temps were low, but the contacts were hot.  Come along as I deploy my @SPOOLTENNA 4010 EFHW and make contacts on 3 bands in support of this special event.
#pota #parksontheair #hamradio #radioantenna #hamradioantenna 

Equipment used:
 @YaesuUSAOfficial  FT-891
 @ABRindCoax  Coax
 @ecoworthy_official  20ah battery
 @LDGElectronics-2  Z-100 plus autotuner
 @JamesHannibalKH2SR  Quirky QRP Mammoth Mat
 @smartlogger  
 @ParksOnTheAir  
 @DXEngineering  
 @GigaPartsHuntsville  
@SPOOLTENNA 

