snippet.description:
After spending my morning with the fantastic folks with the Central Mississippi Amateur Radio Assoc at Lake Lincoln State Park near Brookhaven, MS, I ducked into US-2549 on my way back to the QTH.  This was a quick 2 band activation on Saturday during Support Your Parks weekend.  The bands were packed with POTA activators and contesters.  It was crazy.  This one was special as I make my first ever P2P with @Brent_N4BDW !
#pota #parksontheair #hamradio #radioantenna #portableradio 

Equipment used:
 @YaesuUSAOfficial  FT-891
 @ecoworthy_official  20ah Battery
 @ABRindCoax  Coax
 @LDGElectronics-2   Z-100 plus tuner
 @ParksOnTheAir  
Shark Hamstick 20m & 15m
 @smartlogger  
 @JamesHannibalKH2SR  Quirky QRP Mammoth Mat
 @GigaPartsHuntsville  
 @DXEngineering ​
 @looknorthdesigns  mount

 I appreciate you watching and hope to hear you on the air, FROM A PARK, soon.
73,
Paul

