snippet.description:
It doesn't get much easier than the Gabil CFS-10 Carbon Fiber 10m whip on top of the picnic table. This small footprint setup was amazing.  I completed the activation on 10m in only 12min.  I went on to 15 and 20m by simply removing the CFS-10 and putting my SS-17 whip in it's place. Come along on another fun outing as I try to Keep it Simple because, POTA activating doesn't have to be complicated.
#pota 
#radioantenna 
#parksontheair 
#hamradio 
